      "sacrifices": "Ties saga lifecycle to Order Service's database. Migration of saga ownership later would require data migration.",
      "alternatives_considered": ["Dedicated saga store (separate DB or service): more flexible but adds operational complexity for a 4-step flow that naturally belongs to Order Management."]
    },
